Manchester City lost 2-1 to Crystal Palace at Selhurst Park on Monday night . 
  City have not won a Premier League game having trailed at half-time in almost 20 years . 
  Manuel Pellegrini's side beat Blackburn Rovers 3-2 in April 1995 . 
  The last time City won a game having been behind at half time was on April 17, 1995 . 
 